When Cursor auto-generates a Git commit message for this repository, follow these rules:

Format: `<type>(<scope>): <subject>`

- subject: Korean, concise, no trailing period
- type: feat | fix | refactor | test | chore | docs
- scope (optional): api | batch | domain | frontend | root

Scope guide:
- api → backend/apps/api
- batch → backend/apps/batch
- domain → backend/libs/domain (or libs/entity)
- frontend → frontend/
- root → repo-wide config (gitignore, CI, .github, etc.)
- cross-cutting config: use chore: or chore(root):

Examples:
- feat(api): GitHub OAuth 로그인 구현
- fix(frontend): 히트맵 날짜 오프셋 버그 수정
- refactor(domain): 회고 집계 로직 분리
- chore(root): .gitignore 업데이트
- docs: README 아키텍처 섹션 추가
